  "title": "5 days Electrical Design Engineer up to $5200 (Tuas)",
  "description": "<p>Electrical Design Engineer</p><p>Working Hours: 8.15am – 5.45pm (Mon–Fri)</p><p>Salary: $3,800 – $5,200</p><p>Location: Tuas</p><p>Benefits: AWS, Bonus, 14 days AL</p><p></p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Prepare material requisition lists based on project requirements.</li><li>Design electrical switchboards, consoles, and control panels in accordance with customer specifications and Terasaki standards.</li><li>Prepare approval, shop, and final drawings, technical documents, short-circuit calculations, and manuals.</li><li>Coordinate with clients, consultants, and internal teams on technical matters.</li><li>Review and follow up on design and shop drawings with production to ensure accuracy and compliance.</li><li>Support Sales & Marketing with technical advice, tenders, and variation claims.</li><li>Ensure designs comply with standards, quality requirements, and TQM procedures.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned.</li></ul><p></p><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Electrical Engineering or equivalent.</li><li>Experience in switchboard, console, or control panel design preferred.</li><li>Knowledge of electrical standards, short-circuit calculations, and design documentation.</li><li>Able to prepare and interpret technical drawings and specifications.</li><li>Good communication skills; detail-oriented and proactive.</li><li>Able to work independently and in a team.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Company Name: Talent Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 24C2338</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Loke Sai Lye (Loke)</p><p>EA Personnel No: R24123366</p><p>Email: loke.dexter@talentrecruitmentsg.com</p><p>Contact Number: 8168 8648</p>",
